This is the third in command of the keep guards.
This paladin has a profound aura of confidence. Enivid is the Keep's Hand, though she aspires to greater things.
Feran Fairhand is the intense guildmaster of the military. He takes his duties very seriously.

Dynschall LaVelisi is the hellfire-and-brimstone preacher who heads the priest guild. As the priest of Pharos, the god of Judgment and Lord of Battles, Dynschall oversees the temple and holds great sway over his "flock".
This is Sir Becket, a nobleman of the keep. His ambition far outwieghs any scruples he might have once had.
This is Momma Dane, a friendly old gossip who spends most of her time in the village square. She seems to have taken a liking to you.
Alias is the local messenger girl and scout. She knows her way around the keep and around some of the caves as well.
Manybrick Manor - Haunted - Please see Serah Blackhand.
